description: Non-material amendment to house types shown for Plots 1-8 inclusive and associated alterations to the frontage layout for these plots for planning permission granted under ref 18/00443/FULL1 for the redevelopment of the site to provide 280 residential units (Use Class C3), a Use Class C2 care home for the frail elderly, retention of the sports pavilion, retention of the spine road, provision of open space and associated works.
